<h3>Scale (orders of magnitude)</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Comparing things by factor of 10. Saying "two orders of magnitude bigger" means 100×.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Powers of 10 timeline: 10, 100, 1000, etc.</p>
