<h3>Equilibrium</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> A state of balance where opposing forces or processes cancel out. Earth's climate was in approximate equilibrium for thousands of years until recent change.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A scale with equal weights on both sides.</p>
