</table>

<h3>Erosion</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Movement of weathered material by water, wind, ice, or gravity. Different from weathering (breakdown only).</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A river carrying sediment downhill.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Marina Beach erosion is mostly from waves; some segments are eroding faster than others."</p>
