</table>

<h3>Watershed</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> An area of land where all water drains to a single river, lake, or ocean.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A bowl-shaped landscape with arrows showing water flowing to a low point.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "The Cooum watershed is ~720 km², draining suburban + central Chennai."</p>
