<h2 id="u4">Unit 4 — Atmosphere &amp; Climate <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;">(14 terms)</span></h2>

<h3>Climate change</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Long-term shifts in temperature and weather patterns, primarily caused by human greenhouse gas emissions since the industrial revolution.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Temperature graph trending upward over time, with smoke + industry icons.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Climate change is making Chennai's monsoons more variable and heat waves more intense."</p>
