</table>

<h3>Adaptation</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Changes to deal with climate impacts that are already happening or will happen anyway (sea walls, heat warning systems, drought-resistant crops).</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A city adding seawalls + tree canopy + drainage upgrades.</p>
