<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Meeting today's needs without compromising future generations' ability to meet theirs.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Three pillars (environment, economy, society) supporting a stable platform.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Bangalore's water use is not currently sustainable — extracting faster than recharge."</p>
