</table>

<h2 id="u6">Unit 6 — Biosphere, Land Use &amp; Food Systems <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;">(12 terms)</span></h2>

<h3>Biosphere</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> All living things on Earth, plus the ecosystems they inhabit. Earth's living layer.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Earth with green vegetation + animals + microorganisms highlighted.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "The biosphere is the most complex of Earth's subsystems, with millions of interacting species."</p>
