</table>

<h3>Biodiversity</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> The variety of life — genetic, species, ecosystem levels. Higher biodiversity often = greater ecosystem resilience.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A forest with many different plant + animal species.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Western Ghats is a biodiversity hotspot with thousands of endemic species."</p>
