</table>

<h3>Ecosystem</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> A community of organisms interacting with each other and their environment. Boundaries can be physical (a pond, a forest) or functional.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A pond with fish, plants, insects, water, sediment all interacting.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "The Cauvery delta is an ecosystem connecting rice paddies, river hydrology, and waterbird populations."</p>
