</table>

<h3>Ecosystem services</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Benefits humans get from ecosystems: provisioning (food, water), regulating (climate, pollination), cultural (recreation, spirituality), supporting (soil, water cycle).</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A forest with arrows showing benefits flowing out: food, water, pollination, climate buffer.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Pallikaranai Marsh provides flood-buffer ecosystem services to southern Chennai."</p>
