</table>

<h3>Land use</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> How a piece of land is used — agriculture, forest, urban, conservation. Land-use decisions are central to environmental policy.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A pie chart of land allocated to different uses.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Iowa land use is dominated by industrial corn-soy agriculture; Western Ghats has more agroforestry."</p>
