</table>

<h3>Multi-objective</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Trying to achieve more than one goal at the same time. Multi-objective design accepts that not all goals can be maximized.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Multiple targets with a single shot trying to hit all of them.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "The Sustainable Land Plan is a multi-objective design — balancing food + biodiversity + climate + equity."</p>
