</table>

<h3>Indigenous</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Original inhabitants of a region. Indigenous knowledge + land rights are increasingly recognized as central to sustainability.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A map showing indigenous territories overlaid on a country.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Indigenous land management in the Amazon often achieves better biodiversity outcomes than government-run conservation."</p>
