</table>

<h3>Renewable</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Energy sources that are replenished by natural processes on human timescales: solar, wind, hydro, geothermal.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Sun, wind turbine, water turbine, geothermal vent.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Tamil Nadu has India's largest installed wind capacity — a major renewable success story."</p>
