</table>

<h3>Fossil fuel</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Energy sources made from ancient organic matter: coal, oil, natural gas. Finite + emit greenhouse gases.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Coal mine, oil rig, natural gas plant.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "India's electricity is still ~70% from fossil fuels (mostly coal)."</p>
