</table>

<h3>Grid</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> The network of electricity infrastructure — power plants, transmission lines, substations, distribution lines — that delivers electricity.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A web of power lines connecting generation to homes + businesses.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Chennai's electricity grid must balance supply + demand minute-by-minute."</p>
