<h3>Decarbonization</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Reducing carbon emissions across the economy. Different from net-zero (which includes removals) — focuses on cutting emissions.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A graph of emissions trending downward over time.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Decarbonization requires changes across electricity + industry + transport + buildings + agriculture."</p>
