<h3>Op-Ed</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> An opinion-editorial article — a short, audience-aware argument piece for general newspapers or magazines. Different from academic essay.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> A newspaper page with an opinion column highlighted.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Your Op-Ed should sound like a published newspaper op-ed, not like a school essay."</p>
