<h3>Just transition</h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong> Energy transition that protects workers + communities affected by the shift away from fossil fuels. Recognizes social costs of change.</p>
<p><strong>Visual cue:</strong> Coal workers transitioning to renewable energy jobs.</p>
<p><strong>In a sentence:</strong> "Cape Town's coal transition requires just-transition strategies for affected mining communities."</p>
